38-709.Certified registered nurse anesthetist; license; renewal.

To renew a license to practice as a certified registered nurse anesthetist, the applicant shall have current certification by the Council on Certification of Nurse Anesthetists.

SourceLaws 1981, LB 379, § 32;Laws 1993, LB 536, § 73;Laws 1995, LB 563, § 42;Laws 1996, LB 414, § 46;Laws 1999, LB 828, § 157;Laws 2000, LB 1115, § 61;Laws 2002, LB 1021, § 62;Laws 2003, LB 242, § 106;Laws 2005, LB 256, § 80;R.S.Supp.,2006, § 71-1735;Laws 2007, LB185, § 18;Laws 2007, LB463, § 239.
